com.google.inject.multibindings

Interface MultibindingsTargetVisitor<T,V>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BindingTargetVisitor<T,V>

    public interface MultibindingsTargetVisitor<T,V>
extends BindingTargetVisitor<T,V>
    A visitor for the multibinder extension.

    If your BindingTargetVisitor implements this interface, bindings created by using Multibinder, MapBinder or OptionalBinderBinding will be visited through this interface.

    Since:
    3.0
